Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.76,0:00:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去床上睡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.56,0:00:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想吵醒你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.80,0:01:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.64,0:01:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很晚了明天要早起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.32,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你躺着就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.88,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可爱吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 先戴套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.92,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.16,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生小孩要有计划性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.36,0:05:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟伯父外遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.20,0:06:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.72,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大白天就在喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退休后太闲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要伯父陪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不你又变漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.16,0:06:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去买点小菜回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道  早买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.36,0:06:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我们吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉呀   白天的酒真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然要配下酒菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该生小孩了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会一直没小孩唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这的确是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆这么漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓住机会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊要趁年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.04,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊\N又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也很披心你们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结婚后变更美咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你伯父很早就认识了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有他我才可以这么安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.04,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么烦恼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟我说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.72,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像有两个老爸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.40,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像回到年轻时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.80,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的年龄已经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.40,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传来了\N（前辈  今天很开心  你真的很棒呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.36,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（前辈  今天很开心 你真的很棒呢）\N（我今天也很开心）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏月跟小诚怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫麦就是要沟通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以告诉我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在劝她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  可以告诉我到底怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  要你陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会啊  我喜欢荞麦面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.48,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.16,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸很生气唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.92,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏月啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别难过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.76,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种外遇的烂男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.16,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他分手   找个更好的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.76,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那伯父跟我在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你躺下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.44,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因为对方外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也不想回你那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让她待我这吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让她待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来就会回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.32,0:15:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很好吃唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的料理啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.76,0:15:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不结婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.36,0:15:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人不结婚的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.52,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你喜欢这种啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.88,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小孩该看的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.48,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩\N好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.36,0:16:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去洗澡\N饭怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起洗吧\N少说笨活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候不是常一起洗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚明明就说我是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先吃饭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你洗背\N别说笨话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.92,0:18:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么费心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.72,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前常一 起洗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.76,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不是小孩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚不是说我是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.28,0:18:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱找借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N很好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也帮你洗前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边就不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.92,0:19:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么笨话啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.08,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己洗就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.88,0:20:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.12,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我老公完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.92,0:20:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我要自己洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要冲水咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.48,0:21:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲好咯\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.08,0:21:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面也让我看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.04,0:21:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开我\N让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想报恩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.52,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老公完全不夸我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.48,0:22:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.36,0:22:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父好可爱\N住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.20,0:23:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.68,0:23:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.56,0:23:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.60,0:23:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变好硬唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.20,0:23:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看伯父的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.36,0:24:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.16,0:24:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.96,0:24:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.00,0:25:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来让你更爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.20,0:25:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.44,0:26:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.64,0:26:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.20,0:26:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父手拿开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.56,0:26:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.76,0:27:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.56,0:27:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.16,0:28:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.00,0:28:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.16,0:29:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.52,0:29:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.56,0:30:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.08,0:30:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.60,0:31:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.24,0:31:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.80,0:31:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.52,0:32:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.88,0:32:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回家时也跟爸一起睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.32,0:32:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.52,0:32:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.76,0:33:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.64,0:33:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.67,0:33:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.40,0:33:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.56,0:34:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.36,0:35:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏月...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.60,0:35:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.24,0:36:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.84,0:37:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.92,0:38:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.88,0:38:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.88,0:38:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.04,0:40:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.40,0:40:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.72,0:42:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.36,0:42:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.36,0:42:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:39.32,0:42:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.04,0:43:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.40,0:44:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父
