Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.52,0:59:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:48.68,0:59:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.48,0:59:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N等她想回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.16,1:00:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.16,1:00:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吃什么啊?\N吃水果
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:22.92,1:00:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在讲话别吃东西啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.36,1:00:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.36,1:00:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.08,1:00:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等她冷静下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.12,1:01:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.68,1:01:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:10.44,1:01:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:19.08,1:01:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:29.32,1:01:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.44,1:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在听
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:38.44,1:01:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.00,1:02:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.48,1:02:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.08,1:02:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能交给时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:16.68,1:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再打给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.72,1:02:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.92,1:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.36,1:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:26.76,1:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
