Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:25.64,1:10:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:29.80,1:11:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用吞下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.32,1:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是很担心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:07.72,1:12:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  随她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:13.32,1:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父人真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:19.88,1:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老公有跟你连络吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:22.92,1:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没说我在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.16,1:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在别的女人那吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.64,1:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是烂人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.52,1:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡下了吗？\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.48,1:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:55.08,1:12:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太逞强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:25.16,1:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.08,1:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸在那边耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:49.16,1:13:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啦\N没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.12,1:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父好好闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.88,1:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗?
