Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.80,1:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.72,1:25:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也睡下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:00.52,1:26:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去床上睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:20.36,1:26:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.20,1:26:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我鬼迷心窍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:27.24,1:26:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.92,1:26:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:37.64,1:26:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说谁都会犯错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:42.28,1:26:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以后不会再犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:46.92,1:26:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我怎么相信你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.24,1:26:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你赔偿费
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:57.64,1:27:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要调职到国外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:02.12,1:27:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水比现在更高
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:07.40,1:27:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要去那边三年，
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:10.76,1:27:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来后就可以当部长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:14.92,1:27:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我一直没讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:20.36,1:27:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你一直想要小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:26.12,1:27:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没跟我商量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:29.80,1:27:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你怀孕的话   搬家会很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:33.48,1:27:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着小孩也很麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.00,1:27:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你在讲\N我希望你跟我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.72,1:27:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了   别追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.52,1:32:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:46.60,1:33:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:29.64,1:36:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来让你更爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:28.52,1:37:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
