Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:01.16,1:56:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我3年后一定 会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:08.20,1:56:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:12.52,1:56:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:48.20,1:56:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯父  谢谢你
